    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Daniel Mendoza",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.21,
      "endTime": 9.92
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "How many unsuccessful attempts did Mendoza make before becoming Champion of all England?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.93,
      "endTime": 18.58,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "How",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "怎样，如何"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Boxing matches were very popular in England two hundred years ago.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 18.59,
      "endTime": 23.51,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In those days, boxers fought with bare fists for prize money.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 23.52,
      "endTime": 28.92
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Because of this, they were known as 'prizefighters'.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.93,
      "endTime": 33.26,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "However, boxing was very crude,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.27,
      "endTime": 36.62,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "for there were no rules and a prizefighter could be seriously injured or even killed during a match.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.63,
      "endTime": 44.93
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "One of the most colourful figures in boxing history was Daniel Mendoza, who was born in 1764.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 44.94,
      "endTime": 53.55
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The use of gloves was not introduced until 1860, when the Marquis of Queensberry drew up the first set of rules.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 53.56,
      "endTime": 62.62,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Though he was technically a prizefighter,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 62.63,
      "endTime": 65.74
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Mendoza did much to change crude prizefighting into a sport, for he brought science to the game.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 65.75,
      "endTime": 73.7,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "In his day, Mendoza enjoyed tremendous popularity.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 73.71,
      "endTime": 78.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He was adored by rich and poor alike.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 78.41,
      "endTime": 81.93
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Mendoza rose to fame swiftly after a boxing match when he was only fourteen years old.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 81.94,
      "endTime": 88.41,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Old",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "老的，旧的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This attracted the attention of Richard Humphries who was then the most eminent boxer in England.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.42,
      "endTime": 95.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He offered to train Mendoza and his young pupil was quick to learn.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 95.87,
      "endTime": 100.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Young",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "年轻的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In fact, Mendoza soon became so successful that Humphries turned against him.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 100.98,
      "endTime": 108,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The two men quarrelled bitterly and it was clear that the argument could only be settled by a fight.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 108.01,
      "endTime": 116.49,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "A match was held at Stilton, where both men fought for an hour.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 116.5,
      "endTime": 121.59,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The public bet a great deal of money on Mendoza, but he was defeated.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 121.6,
      "endTime": 127.21
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Mendoza met Humphries in the ring on a later occasion and he lost for a second time.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 127.22,
      "endTime": 133.96
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It was not until his third match in 1790 that he finally beat Humphries and became Champion of England.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 133.97,
      "endTime": 143.49,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Meanwhile, he founded a highly successful Academy and even Lord Byron became one of his pupils.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 143.5,
      "endTime": 151.58,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He earned enormous sums of money and was paid as much as ￡100 for a single appearance.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 151.59,
      "endTime": 159.84,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Despite this, he was so extravagant that he was always in debt.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 159.85,
      "endTime": 165.9,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "After he was defeated by a boxer called Gentleman Jackson, he was quickly forgotten.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 165.91,
      "endTime": 172.52
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He was sent to prison for failing to pay his debts and died in poverty in 1836.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 172.53,
      "endTime": 177.53,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    }
  ]
}
